+# Gaussian belief over SE(3) pose for SQUARE/0.2 (gaussian_se3 representation).
+# Mean:       standard ROS pose (TUM-compatible: tx, ty, tz, qx, qy, qz, qw).
+# Covariance: 6x6 in IKFoM-native tangent space, row-major.
+#   TANGENT_CONVENTION: right_perturbation
+#   TANGENT_ORDER:      translation_rotation  (pos at [0..2], rot at [3..5])
+#   ROTATION_PARAM:     axis_angle
+# gauge: which DoF the algorithm pinned by initialization
+#        ('fixed' | 'se3' | 'gravity_yaw' | 'sim3'). Set by the publishing node.
+Header header
+geometry_msgs/Pose pose
+float64[36] covariance
+string gauge
